<p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='251:277'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0084', 'WYG', '128-3a' );" name="128-3a" class="pb">[128-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
